description:
Create src/components/tick-header.ts:

@customElement('tick-header')
export class TickHeader extends LitElement {
  @property() repoName: string = '';
  @property({ type: Array }) epics: string[] = [];
  @property() selectedEpic: string = '';
  @property() searchTerm: string = '';
}

Features using Shoelace components:
- Repository name display
- sl-input for search with search icon, debounced input event
- sl-select for epic filter dropdown populated from epics list
- sl-button for 'Create Tick' action
- Emit events: 'search-change', 'epic-filter-change', 'create-click'

Test: Render header, interact with search/filter, verify events fire
